<ul><li>A <b>known mass</b> of liquid in an&nbsp;<b>insulated calorimeter</b>&nbsp;of known mass and known specific heat capacity.</li><li>An&nbsp;<b>electrical heater</b>&nbsp;placed in the liquid is used to heat the liquid directly.</li><li>A&nbsp;<b>thermometer</b>&nbsp;inserted into the liquid is used to measure the&nbsp;<b>temperature rise</b>.</li></ul>